{"prompt": "Build a portfolio for a freelance editor. The overall look should be precise, incorporating a mustard yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Freelance Editor Portfolio</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #d4a017; /* Mustard Yellow */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #555 3px solid;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        header p {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n        #main-content {\n            padding: 30px 0;\n        }\n        #main-content h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #d4a017;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        .service-item, .portfolio-item {\n            background: #fff;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border-left: 5px solid #d4a017;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .service-item h3, .portfolio-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #d4a017;\n        }\n        .portfolio-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            display: block;\n            margin: 15px 0;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #d4a017;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 80%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background: #d4a017;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background: #b8860b;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Clarity in Every Word</h1>\n            <p>Your Freelance Editor for Precision and Polish</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Me</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <p>I am a dedicated freelance editor with a passion for refining text, ensuring clarity, consistency, and grammatical accuracy. My meticulous approach guarantees that your content shines with professionalism and impact.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Copyediting</h3>\n                <p>Enhancing readability and flow while correcting grammar, spelling, punctuation, and syntax.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Proofreading</h3>\n                <p>A final check for any remaining errors before publication.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Developmental Editing</h3>\n                <p>Focusing on the big picture: structure, plot, character development, and overall coherence.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"portfolio\">\n            <h2>Portfolio Highlights</h2>\n            <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                <h3>Book Manuscript - Fiction</h3>\n                <p>Collaborated with an emerging author to polish their debut novel, focusing on character arcs and pacing. The book was subsequently picked up by a small press.</p>\n                <!-- Placeholder for an image if available -->\n                <!-- <img src=\"path/to/book_cover.jpg\" alt=\"Book Cover Example\"> -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                <h3>Website Content - Tech Startup</h3>\n                <p>Edited and refined website copy for a growing tech company, ensuring brand voice consistency and clear communication of their services to a wider audience.</p>\n                 <!-- Placeholder for an image if available -->\n                <!-- <img src=\"path/to/website_screenshot.jpg\" alt=\"Website Content Example\"> -->\n            </div>\n             <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                <h3>Academic Paper - Journal Publication</h3>\n                <p>Provided comprehensive editing for a research paper, ensuring adherence to academic standards and facilitating successful publication in a peer-reviewed journal.</p>\n                 <!-- Placeholder for an image if available -->\n                <!-- <img src=\"path/to/academic_paper.jpg\" alt=\"Academic Paper Example\"> -->\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <p>Let's discuss your project. Send me a message!</p>\n                <form action=\"mailto:your.email@example.com\" method=\"post\" enctype=\"text/plain\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required><br>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required><br>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea><br>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Freelance Editor. All rights reserved. | Contact: <a href=\"mailto:your.email@example.com\">your.email@example.com</a></p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}